Resource Profile: 事前審查品項-MedicationRequest Apply TWPAS

Official URL: https://nhicore.nhi.gov.tw/pas/StructureDefinition/MedicationRequest-apply-twpas Version: 1.0.6
Active as of 2025-07-30 Computable Name: MedicationRequestApplyTWPAS

此事前審查品項-MedicationRequest Apply TWPAS Profile說明本IG如何進一步定義臺灣核心-藥品請求(TW Core MedicationRequest) Profile以呈現癌藥事前審查中申請項目之事前審查品項

Usages:

  • Use this Profile: 事前審查-Bundle TWPAS
  • Refer to this Profile: RequestedService
  • Examples for this Profile: MedicationRequest/medReq-apply-2 and MedicationRequest/medReq-apply
  • CapabilityStatements using this Profile: 臺灣癌藥事前審查-用戶端(TWPAS Client) and 臺灣癌藥事前審查-伺服端(TWPAS Server)

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
